name: QAnon Shaman
description:
follow me on Instagram, Youtube and my website.

QAnon Shaman

Suggested Weight: 0.6-1.2 (this is where the embedding shines imo, you can dial it up or down as much as you need, depending on how well it's mixing with the other subject)

Suggested prompts

  • portrait photo of (man:1.0) as (q4n0n5h4m4n:0.9), horns, facepaint

  • portrait photo of (man:1.0) as (female q4n0n5h4m4n:0.9), horns, facepaint

  • portrait photo of (man:1.0) as (q4n0n5h4m4n:0.9), horns:0.3, facepaint:0.6

To give someone horns, you usually need to add horns to the prompt, which depending on the subject and rest of the prompt might need to be weighted up or down (too high will turn them into a goat, too low won't render horns at all).

Also facepaint can be most specific like patriotic facepaint

Training

  • trained on ~12 images

  • Learning Rate: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0001:5000, 0.00005

  • Batch Size: 1

  • Gradient Steps: 1
